---
---

<div class="section-container">
  <div class="open-roles-section">
    <h2 class="sub-heading">Open roles</h2>
    <p class="roles-intro">
      We are looking for a mission-driven UI/UX designer to help shape how people experience&nbsp;Nepal&nbsp;Climate&nbsp;Hub&nbsp;online.
    </p>

    <div class="roles-grid">
      <article class="role-card" data-role="ui-ux-designer">
        <header class="role-card__head">
          <div class="role-card__title-block">
            <h3 class="role-title">UI/UX Designer</h3>
            <div class="role-badges" role="list">
              <span class="role-badge" role="listitem">2 openings</span>
              <span class="role-badge role-badge--muted" role="listitem"
                >3–6 months</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </header>

        <p class="role-lead">
          Help us craft intuitive, accessible interfaces for our platform and
          campaigns—so climate information feels clear, engaging, and
          actionable for young people in Nepal and beyond.
        </p>

        <div class="role-content">
          <section class="role-panel" aria-labelledby="role-do-heading">
            <h4 id="role-do-heading" class="role-panel__title">What you&rsquo;ll do</h4>
            <ul class="role-list">
              <li>Design user-friendly flows and screens for web (and mobile where relevant).</li>
              <li>Create wireframes, mockups, and prototypes—usually in Figma or similar.</li>
              <li>Partner with content, storytelling, and engineering so designs ship smoothly.</li>
              <li>Use design to make climate topics easier to understand and act on.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="role-panel" aria-labelledby="role-look-heading">
            <h4 id="role-look-heading" class="role-panel__title">What we&rsquo;re looking for</h4>
            <ul class="role-list">
              <li>Comfort with a modern design tool (e.g. Figma, Adobe XD).</li>
              <li>User-centered thinking: clarity, hierarchy, and accessibility.</li>
              <li>Collaboration, feedback, and attention to detail.</li>
              <li>Interest in climate, youth, or social impact (no need to be an expert).</li>
              <li>Bonus: experience with design systems or component libraries.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </div>

        <footer class="role-card__foot">
          <a
            href="https://forms.gle/P2VEUBQMdie3rgp56"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="apply-button apply-button--wide"
            aria-label="Apply for UI/UX Designer role"
          >
            Apply for this role
          </a>
          <p class="role-footnote">
            Questions? Email{' '}
            <a href="mailto:info@nepalclimatehub.org">info@nepalclimatehub.org</a>
          </p>
        </footer>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .section-container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    margin-bottom: 120px;
  }

  .open-roles-section {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .sub-heading {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.5vw, 28px);
    line-height: 1.25;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #1a1b1e;
  }

  .roles-intro {
    max-width: none;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    color: #4b5563;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .roles-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .role-card {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e8eaed;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: clamp(22px, 4vw, 32px);
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 2px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04),
      0 8px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    transition:
      box-shadow 0.25s ease,
      border-color 0.25s ease;
  }

  .role-card:hover {
    border-color: #d4e85a;
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 2px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06),
      0 12px 32px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
  }

  .role-card__head {
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f3f5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .role-card__title-block {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: min(100%, 220px);
  }

  .role-title {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.8vw, 26px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1b1e;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .role-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .role-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #cefe00;
    color: #1a1b1e;
  }

  .role-badge--muted {
    background: #f1f3f5;
    color: #495057;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .apply-button:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid #364fc7;
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .apply-button:active {
    transform: scale(0.99);
  }

  .role-lead {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #495057;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }

  .role-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(16px, 3vw, 28px);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .role-panel {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 18px 18px 20px;
    border: 1px solid #eef0f2;
  }

  .role-panel__title {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1b1e;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .role-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.15rem;
  }

  .role-list li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #374151;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .role-list li:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .role-list li::marker {
    color: #364fc7;
  }

  .role-card__foot {
    padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px solid #f1f3f5;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .apply-button--wide {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: #cefe00;
    color: #1a1b1e;
    transition:
      background 0.2s ease,
      transform 0.15s ease;
  }

  .apply-button--wide:hover {
    background: #b8e600;
    color: #1a1b1e;
  }

  .role-footnote {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #6b7280;
    text-align: start;
  }

  .role-footnote a {
    color: #364fc7;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .role-footnote a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1280px) {
    .section-container {
      padding: 40px 48px;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-container {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .role-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
    .role-card {
      padding: 20px 18px;
      border-radius: 16px;
    }

    .role-panel {
      padding: 16px;
    }
  }
</style>
